# pmi-core configuration moved to the platform-root single source of truth:
#   /Users/reid/micah/pmi_data_platform/.env
#
# This file is kept only as a pointer; pmi-core's pydantic-settings probes
# all three of: cwd `.env`, this service-root `.env` (legacy), and the
# platform-root `pmi_data_platform/.env` (current).
#
# pmi-core specifically reads the following keys (prefixed `PMI_`):
#   - PMI_DB_HOST / PMI_DB_PORT / PMI_DB_NAME / PMI_DB_USER / PMI_DB_PASSWORD / PMI_DB_SSL
#   - OPENAI_API_KEY (Sprint 2: real LLM evaluator)
#   - PMI_MLFLOW_TRACKING_URI / PMI_MLFLOW_ENABLED / PMI_MLFLOW_EXPERIMENT_PREFIX
#   - PMI_LOG_LEVEL
#
# Bootstrap a fresh checkout:
#   cp pmi_data_platform/.env.example pmi_data_platform/.env
